item.title: League of Legends
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

[quote=“Mopman, post:7, topic:386977”]US and EU, both Mopman, plus my first account that I never play anymore anyway

I change my champions basically as I change my underwear, mostly playing Rammus and Annie atm, with a bit of Ashe thrown in when I’m solo queueing because for some reason I find it easy to stomp pubs with her the majority of the time.

Thinking of buying Vlad, but I somehow never got to try him in a free week, he just looks fun. Not sure if the nerfs wrecked him or not though.

TF is fuckin hilarious, but I get stick of being #1 focus all the time through playing so many squishies, so I’m rarely in the mood to play him tbh… the ganking is great, but teamfights can be a bit frustrating.

EDIT: How do you find Malzahar? I’m considering him instead of Vlad tbh.[/quote]
Malzahar is by far the best AP hero for sure. Though you could debate that with Viegar, but I’d prefer Malzahar. Only because Malzahar is excellent early, mid and even better end game if you have a good build.

I don’t see what everyone likes about Vlad, I’ve tried every champion more than 3 games each and I don’t really like Vlad actually. I own every champion except Nocturne right now. The nerfs appear to of only ruined Cho’Gath lately.

Read full topic
